{"tid":1779814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓國瑜：非高雄人不要管高雄事","createTime":"2019-12-12T02:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T05:39:33.000Z","uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f27063e329a5b3fed3fb715947150ba75593f778","tid":1779814,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導〕國民黨總統候選人韓國瑜11日在高雄「南方崛起高雄光榮一週年」記者會上，公開呼籲罷韓大遊行主辦單位「不要用遊覽車帶外縣市的人來高雄」，更指稱「把這些人用遊覽車載來高雄是嚴重污辱高雄市民的智慧」。對此，台北市議員苗博雅相當不滿，直批韓「你根本忘記自己是高雄市長了」？<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜11日在受訪時向罷韓大遊行主辦單位隔空呼籲「千千萬萬不要用遊覽車帶外縣市的人來高雄」，更強烈指出「絕不容許外縣市的人來高雄參與罷免高雄市市長這樣子的遊行」，還指稱若把人用遊覽車載到高雄市是「嚴重污辱高雄市民的智慧」。<br />\n<br />\n苗博雅對韓國瑜言論相當疑惑，認為既然韓國瑜做出如此要求，那選高雄市長造勢時為何不叫其他縣市的支持者不要去？為何不呼籲沒投票權的小朋友青少年不要參加挺韓造勢？<br />\n<br />\n苗博雅認為，既然韓國瑜要玩「非高雄人不要管高雄事」，那為何韓國瑜「開口閉口就跟中央要錢、跟全國納稅人要錢？」她憤怒表示，明年中央將補助高雄451億，都是來自全國納稅人，韓國瑜卻好意思說外縣市的人沒資格管你，「還是你根本忘記自己是高雄市長了？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3006109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3006109&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnADv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=13f444bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3006109&h=97322fae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3006109</a>"},{"pid":"b6edd244f0a99e42766ae9e2cebf162100882e79","tid":1779814,"uid":11254,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜（1957年6月17日－），中華民國政治人物，中國國民黨籍，生於今<span style=\"color: red;\">新北市中和區</span>"},{"pid":"4a3b126aba6dd3541e331577e4812eed514b54b8","tid":1779814,"uid":325556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"干涉「別市」內政"},{"pid":"c6b18cd14a72e2a499710543c7fc42e76d4382ca","tid":1779814,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:23:19.000Z","msg":"中國人：中國台灣高雄是中國一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4065653f96582bc44d1f2e91842e9a9f2e4263ee","tid":1779814,"uid":8033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yuq224K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuq224K.jpg&h=dffd6db4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76sXRX6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76sXRX6.jpg&h=9a59e8da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5023dc8865f7a691ed85c557d37bb5ce8a6abcbb","tid":1779814,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:26:44.000Z","msg":"嚴重污辱高雄市民的智慧<br />\n話自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d79d5ad9bd02c230712f4ef94eea25a97ce2a5d","tid":1779814,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"高雄國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e570d7bd21d6e299bc007622481cdd0872685c","tid":1779814,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"支那概念<br />\n一方面想開放市場同世界connect<br />\n但有事就唔比外界comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}